OL,5, Labour has unveiled plans to teach     
OL,6, "real world" maths skills in primary   
OL,7, schools.                               
OL,9,FShadow education secretary Bridget     
OL,10,FPhilipson will say in a speech that    
OL,11,Fchildren as young as four should learn 
OL,12,Ffinancial literacy - including         
OL,13,Fbudgeting and currency exchange rates. 
OL,15,FUnder plans teachers will get extra    
OL,16,Ftraining funded by ending some tax     
OL,17,Fbreaks for private schools.            
OL,19,FLabour say the plans will "bring maths 
OL,20,Fto life" for pupils.                   
